        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">One of our best spells... an 18 second Mez (not a stun).</P><P>If your group gets 2 mobs... pick the one to mez... cast ST,<BR>sick pet on other... count to 10, cast ST on the mez one, <BR>switch, deflux, back to first ST.. etc</P><P>You can cast and recast..... I kept a ranger i was dueling <BR>mezzed for about 6 minutes.. just ST,ST,ST.</P><P>I usually cast at a 10 count, this gives me about 1 recast if I get<BR>a resist.</P><P>Was in a group in Velks the other day, with 2 necros we kept the group alive<BR>mezzing all day, working up to about a 5 spider pull.</P><P>Once the group is ready to pick the next mob to hit (ie. the one you have ST'd)<BR>then you just FD before they hit it to clear aggro... once they have beat on<BR>it for a bit.. get up and attack as normal.</P><P>Remember to back off your pet before the first mob is done, otherwise it will<BR>start hitting the second one right away, if you aren't ready for it.. the mob<BR>will come right to you...</P><P>Played right, most groups Love Necros !</P><P>Muza</P><P><BR> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
